      <strong class="text-cyan-400">Overview:</strong> §21 specifies how a RCAN-compliant robot runtime integrates with an external Robot Registry
      (such as the <a href="https://robotregistryfoundation.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-cyan-400 hover:underline">Robot Registry Foundation</a>).
